channel.title: Anyone wish to start a server with me?
channel.description:
(if this is in the wrong section sorry and move it please)
Ok yeah I'd like some people to start a server with me. First of all you know i'm serious if I don't speak such as "OMG DUD3 ST41RT SW3VER M3 PL0X". And the people that start it with me I expect the same. I am serious as shit about this server and I expect my applicants to be the same.
What I'm really looking for is one coder to help me code. And a couple admins and mods to look over the server. In fact, the coder is practically the second owner.
What I'll be doing: I can host 24/7,No Hamachi,Its run on a damn good computer. Coding-With my other guy. Making our website. And making different things just for us. Add my MSN zachyboy1@hotmail.com for more information or if your interested and or if you don't feel for an application.
Also I'm looking for a few mods and admins.
Admins needed: 0/2
Mods needed: 0/3
Coders needed: 0/1
